%20Delta%20flight%20was%20larger%20and%20a%20bit%20cushier%20than%20the%20seat%20on%20my%20Alaska%20flight.%20The%20Delta%20Airbus%20A321neo%20economy%20seats%20are%2018%20inches%20wide%20with%20a%2031-inch%20seat%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seatguru.com%2Fairlines%2FAlaska_Airlines%2FAlaska_Airlines_Boeing_737-900_D.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Seat%20Guru%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Alaska's%20economy%20seats%20are%2017%20inches%20wide%20and%20have%20a%20seat%20pitch%20between%2031%20and%2032%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta's%20similar%20Boeing%20737-900%20planes%20have%2017.3-inch-wide%20seats%20and%20the%20same%20seat%20pitch%20as%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDelta%20had%20a%20better%20entertainment%20system.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20an%20in-flight%20entertainment%20screen%20and%20a%20seat%20back%20with%20no%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686c01aef748d8c055f5146f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeat%20backs%20in%20economy%20on%20the%20Delta%20and%20Alaska%20flights.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20difference%20between%20my%20experiences%20on%20these%20two%20flights%20was%20the%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Delta%20flight%2C%20I%20had%20a%20seat-back%20touchscreen%20housing%20hundreds%20of%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%20On%20the%20Alaska%20flight%2C%20I%20had%20access%20to%20over%20800%20shows%20and%20movies%20from%20my%20personal%20device%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20seat-back%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20fly%2C%20I%20prefer%20to%20have%20a%20seat-back%20entertainment%20system%20for%20viewing%20because%20it's%20much%20larger%20than%20my%20phone%20screen%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20hold%20it%20up%20in%20front%20of%20my%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20flights%20had%20power%20outlets%2C%20and%20at%20least%20two%20of%20Delta's%20similar%20Boeing%20737-900%20models%20also%20have%20seat-back%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBoth%20flights%20had%20three%20bathrooms%20in%20the%20main%20cabin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20two%20airplane%20bathrooms%20from%20a%20birds-eye%20view%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866af4af748d8c055f4f14b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEconomy%20bathrooms%20on%20the%20Delta%20and%20Alaska%20flights.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20notice%20any%20significant%20differences%20between%20the%20bathrooms.%20Both%20were%20decently%20clean%20and%20expectedly%20cramped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20Delta%20flight%20was%20a%20better%20ride.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Delta%20flight%20parked%20on%20a%20tarmac%20with%20mountains%20behind%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d2ca9f748d8c055f5258a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20preferred%20the%20Delta%20flight.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delta%20flight%20was%20obviously%20more%20enjoyable%20since%20the%20flight%20had%20many%20empty%20seats.%20But%20if%20the%20roles%20were%20reversed%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20back%20middle%20seat%20of%20the%20Delta%20flight%20as%20I%20did%20on%20the%20Alaska%20flight%2C%20I%20still%20think%20I%20would%20have%20preferred%20the%20same%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20larger%2C%20cozier%20seat%20and%20a%2010-inch%20screen%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20I'd%20take%20any%20basic%20economy%20seat%20on%20a%20Delta%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentat