ption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMichael%20McCready%20hopes%20to%20retire%20in%20a%20few%20years%20and%20wanted%20a%20new%20home%20base.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%20decided%20on%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20and%20have%20been%20enjoying%20the%20beach%20and%20weather%20so%20far.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20power%20outages%20and%20higher%20home%20prices%2C%20McCready%20is%20happy%20with%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20conversations%20with%20Michael%20McCready%2C%2056%2C%20a%20lawyer%20who%20moved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20in%20January.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20personal%20injury%20lawyer%20in%20Chicago%20for%2030%20years%2C%20and%20on%20January%201st%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20relocated%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20permanently%20as%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20got%20us%20to%20that%20point%20was%20I'm%2056%2C%20and%20we%20started%20talking%20about%20me%20being%20out%20of%20the%20active%20practice%20of%20law%20at%2060%20and%20traveling.%20My%20wife%20said%20we%20still%20need%20a%20home%20base.%20That%20was%20the%20main%20impetus%20for%20looking%20into%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20beach%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6876952285e81483682e0d2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20beach%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michael%20McCready%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20absolutely%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20we've%20been%20living%20here%20for%20seven%20months%20now.%20I%20come%20back%20to%20Chicago%20periodically%20to%20run%20my%20office%2C%20and%20I%20speak%20around%20the%20country%2C%20but%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20our%20home