rump-china-trade-war-list-of-goods-tariffs-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS-China%20trade%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raised%20costs%20for%20Williams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20Williams%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20long-term%20change%3A%20He%20started%20buying%20products%20from%20as%20many%20sources%20as%20possible%20other%20than%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20years%20later%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20lowered%20the%20share%20of%20materials%20his%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusinesses-cost-moving-supply-chains-out-china-trump-tariff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuys%20from%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2032%25%20down%20to%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20continues%20in%20his%20second%20term%2C%20Williams%20said%20Batteries%20Plus'%20decreased%20reliance%20on%20products%20from%20China%20has%20prevented%20much%20of%20the%20scrambling%20that%20Trump's%20tariffs%20have%20caused%20at%20other%20companies%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2458236-b9b5-43d7-9cbc-179c04898af2%5C%22%3EBatteries%20Plus%20turned%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Vietnam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20companies%20and%20investors%20are%20fretting%20over%20Trump's%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-stock-market-picks-copper-nvda-nike-china-trade-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAugust%201%20deadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20hiking%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20China%2C%20Batteries%20Plus%20has%20a%20diversified%20supplier%20base%20that%20it%20said%20insulates%20it%20from%20some%20of%20these%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20has%20obviously%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20benefit%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatteries%20Plus%20found%20factories%20in%20other%20countries%20to%20replace%20what%20it%20previously%20imported%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20challenge%20was%20finding%20equivalents%20produced%20outside%20China%20that%20were%20of%20the%20same%20quality%2C%20Williams%20said.%20Car%20batteries%20that%20the%20retailer%20produces%20under%20its%20own%20X2%20brand%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20now%20come%20from%20Malaysia%20and%20Vietnam%20because%20Batteries%20Plus%20was%20able%20to%20find%20suppliers%20in%20those%20countries%20that%20matched%20what%20their%20China-based%20suppliers%20could%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20very%20careful%20to%20ensure%20that%2C%20because%20quality%20is%20your%20reputation%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatteries%20Plus%20didn't%20rely%20on%20a%20single%20country%20to%20replace%20what%20it%20used%20to%20import%20from%20China.%20Of%20the%2032%25%20that%20came%20from%20China%20in%202018%2C%20about%2012%20percentage%20points%20now%20come%20from%20Vietnam%2C%208%20from%20US%20sources%2C%205%20from%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20from%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20distribution%20was%20deliberate%2C%20Williams%20said%2C%20so%20that%20the%20company%20could%20shift%20between%20suppliers%20in%20the%20future%20depending%20on%20which%20countries%20are%20hit%20by%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20strategy%20was%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20diversify%20with%20key%20partners%20so%20that%20I%20can%20press%20the%20brake%20or%20the%20accelerator%20on%20different%20countries%20as%20this%20thing%20moves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%204%25%20of%20Batteries%20Plus'%20supplies%20that%20still%20come%20from%20China%20use%20minerals%20that%20the%20company%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20find%20good%20sources%20for%20elsewhere%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20supply%20chain%20strategy%20has%20not%20completely%20shielded%20Batteries%20Plus%20from%20tariffs.%20The%20Trump%20administration%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20targeting%20a%20longer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoiding-trump-tariffs-could-be-harder-companies-countries-vietnam-korea-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elist%20of%20countries%20with%20duties%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20it%20did%20seven%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Trump%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-strikes-vietnam-deal-tariff-nike-lululemon-price-hike-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrade%20deal%20with%20Vietnam%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20subject%20imports%20from%20that%20country%20to%20a%2020%25%20tariff%2C%20up%20from%20the%20current%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20source%20diversification%20has%20helped%20Batteries%20Plus%20avoid%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20tariff%20hikes%20during%20Trump's%20second%20term.%20Tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20China%20briefly%20rose%20to%20145%25%20this%20spring%2C%20dinging%20profit%20at%20companies%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-tree-higher-priced-items-are-helping-it-with-tariffs-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDollar%20Tree%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Cracker%20Barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20said%20that%20Batteries%20Plus%20wants%20to%20pass%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-are-making-some-us-products-more-expensive-data-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20new%20tariffs%20to%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20for%20some%20products%2C%20%26quot%3Bnone%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatteries%20Plus%20has%20also%20used%20other%20cost-cutting%20options%20to%20minimize%20price%20increases.%20The%20company%20has%20increased%20automation%20at%20its%20warehouses%20to%20increase%20efficiency%20and%20negotiated%20with%20suppliers%20to%20minimize%20the%20cost%20of%20tariffs%2C%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20fight%20to%20keep%20prices%20low%2C%20which%20boosts%