I-generated%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20included%20overuse%20of%20robotic%20phrasing%2C%20descriptions%20that%20were%20suspiciously%20vague%20or%20too%20generic%2C%20and%20copy-paste%20energy%20where%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20bullets%20matched%20the%20job%20ad%20word%20for%20word%20or%20used%20the%20same%20language%20at%20the%20start%20of%20each%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lack%20of%20story%20or%20specificity%20becomes%20obvious%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20unique%20insight%2C%20numbers%2C%20or%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20mention%20of%20how%20the%20solution%20was%20delivered%20or%20what%20context%20made%20it%20impressive.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20quickly%20recognized%20certain%20overused%20structures%20that%20contained%20a%20verb%20plus%20a%20buzzword%20and%20a%20measurable%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20noticed%20AI%20was%20flattening%20the%20pool%20of%20applicants%20and%20changing%20the%20job-search%20playing%20field%2C%20so%20he%20needed%20to%20evolve%20his%20hiring%20practices%20both%20as%20a%20Big%20Tech%20hiring%20manager%20and%20a%20career%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20coach%2C%20I%20began%20helping%20people%20adapt%20their%20applications%20to%20avoid%20sounding%20like%20they%20were%20written%20by%20an%20AI%20bot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20strategies%20Anderson%20leveraged%20to%20adjust%20his%20approach%20to%20screening%2C%20interviewing%2C%20and%20hiring%20Big%20Tech%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bda7696b-a219-4bbf-a0d9-8b254507cef2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Moved%20away%20from%20scanning%20for%20keywords%20and%20focused%20on%20proof%20of%20thinking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20dropped%20conventional%20screening%20and%20started%20putting%20less%20stake%20in%20polish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stopped%20looking%20for%20the%20perfect%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20looking%20for%20signs%20they%20actually%20solved%20messy%20problems%2C%20not%20just%20listed%20buzzwords.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20was%20no%20longer%20satisfied%20with%20a%20generic%20statement%20like%20%26quot%3BLed%20a%20cross-functional%20team%20to%20optimize%20workflows.%26quot%3B%20He%20instead%20began%20looking%20for%20statements%20that%20showed%20analytical%20thinking%2C%20not%20just%20task%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a55f13f-4243-4185-bcbc-7fade2042b2a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Rewrote%20interview%20questions%20to%20uncover%20adaptive%20thinking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20a%20candidate%20has%20the%20job%20description%20memorized%2C%20that%20tells%20me%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20see%20how%20they%20think%20when%20the%20script%20disappears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20curveball%20interview%20questions%20that%20required%20interviewees%20to%20think%20on%20their%20feet%2C%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhat's%20a%20decision%20you%20made%20that%20seemed%20right%20at%20the%20time%20but%20didn't%20age%20well%3F%20How%20would%20you%20approach%20it%20now%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EImagine%20we%20just%20launched%20a%20product%20that's%20flopping.%20What's%20your%20first%20step%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20rehearsed%20stories%2C%20these%20questions%20push%20candidates%20to%20think%20in%20real%20time%2C%20especially%20when%20things%20get%20messy%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20you%20uncover%20adaptability%2C%20self-awareness%2C%20and%20problem-solving%20ability.%20This%20is%20about%20how%20they%20think%20through%20imperfection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5472087-ef35-462e-8254-e0257e3fe32f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Prioritized%20signals%20of%20long-term%20learning%20habits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20homed%20in%20to%20find%20candidates%20who%20could%20prove%20their%20substance%2C%20particularly%20through%20their%20approach%20to%20learning%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20adjusted%20to%20focus%20on%20candidates%20with%20continuous%20learning%20habits%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20side%20projects%2C%20cohort-based%20courses%2C%20even%20failures%20%E2%80%94%20over%20polished%20degrees%20or%20'unicorn'%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20said%20that%20while%20AI%20can%20mimic%20experience%2C%20it%20can't%20fake%20curiosity.%20He%20began%20looking%20for%20people%20who%20clearly%20cared%20about%20evolving%20and%20adapting%2C%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreak-into-tech-quit-teaching-coding-boot-camp-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboot%20camp%20grad%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20rebuilt%20their%20job%20search%20process%20based%20on%20feedback%2C%20launched%20a%20small%20internal%20tool%20at%20their%20last%20job%2C%20or%20wrote%20publicly%20about%20what%20they%20were%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20were%20stronger%20indicators%20of%20success%20than%20someone%20who%20simply%20matched%20the%20job%20title%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223aa3a83-bd0c-4940-88fd-e12d728b822e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanity%20is%20a%20Big%20Tech%20candidate's%20competitive%20edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20advocates%20that%20candidates%20add%20personal%20touches%20to%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20AI%20didn't%20write%20it%2C%20like%20an%20'interests'%20section%20with%20personal%20likes%20and%20hobbies.%20He%20added%20that%20these%20details%20need%20to%20be%20specific%20and%20unmistakably%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20enough%20to%20say%20'I%20like%20travel%20and%20cooking'%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20too%20generic%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20share%20something%20only%20you%20could%20say.%26quot%3B%20On%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20he%20used%20to%20s