-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20not%20just%20being%20tired%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20like%20breaking%20from%20the%20inside.%20I%20quit%20abruptly%2C%20with%20no%20plan%2C%20and%20just%20left%20everything%20behind%20because%20I%20could%20not%20take%20it%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20half%20a%20year%2C%20he%20wandered%20through%20a%20haze%20of%20uncertainty.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20who%20I%20was%20outside%20of%20work.%20For%20so%20long%2C%20money%20and%20status%20had%20defined%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20That%20was%20when%20his%20mother%20reminded%20him%20of%20the%20farmland%20he%20had%20bought%20years%20earlier%20near%20Pamidi%20in%20Anantapur%2C%20a%20tract%20of%20red%20earth%20with%20a%20dry%20well.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98You%20always%20wanted%20to%20retire%20on%20a%20farm%2C%E2%80%99%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20start%20now%3F%E2%80%99%20That%20question%20stayed%20with%20me.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20call%20to%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2025-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20started%20to%20experiment%20with%20permaculture%20once%20he%20moved%20to%20his%20farm%20near%20Pamidi%20in%20Anantapur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F202