n-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-6-1752496654.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-6-1752496654-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-6-1752496654-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-6-1752496654-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-6-1752496654-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EInteractive%20workbooks%20and%20teaching%20aids%20help%20teachers%20break%20down%20complex%20topics%20for%20children%20to%20understand%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Smita%20has%20managed%20to%20crack%20the%20code%20is%20because%20of%20her%20holy%20grail%20%E2%80%94%20the%20workbooks%20and%20handbooks%20provided%20to%20her%20by%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation.%20For%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20walking%20into%20class%20armed%20with%20dynamic%20strategies%20%E2%80%94%20a%20radical%20departure%20from%20the%20customary%20methods.%20Weaning%20the%20children%20off%20rote%20learning%2C%20instead%20deploying%20tactile%20aids%2C%20posters%2C%20cue%20cards%2C%20and%20colours%2C%20helps%20break%20the%20ice%20between%20the%20students%20and%20the%20world%20around%20them%20in%20a%20more%20fun%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20is%20it%20working%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spring%20in%20Smita%E2%80%99s%20step%20and%20the%20decibel%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20responses%20suggest%20it%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20used%20to%20teach%20concepts%20in%20the%20usual%20ways.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303196%2Famazon-future-engineer-programme-helps-underprivileged-children-learn-robotics-coding-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOur%20classrooms%20have%20changed%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20our%20school%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation.%20Our%20walls%20are%20now%20filled%20with%20stories%2C%20and%20children%20want%20to%20learn.%20They%20feel%20enthusiastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20workbook%20does%20not%20just%20focus%20on%20questions%20but%20also%20on%20activities.%20I%20teach%20Hindi%20and%20math%3B%20in%20Hindi%2C%20we%20usually%20solve%20the%20vocabulary%20that%20is%20given%20in%20the%20textbooks.%20But%20with%20the%20workbooks%2C%20children%20learn%20how%20to%20identify%20the%20alphabet%20and%20how%20to%20use%20it%20in%20their%20daily%20language.%20The%20books%20give%20us%20different%20ways%20of%20teaching%20them%20poems%20and%20stories.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20these%20thrill%20Jhingran.%20It%E2%80%99s%20antithetical%20to%20the%20reality%20that%20he%20watched%20unfolding%20in%20the%20classrooms%20of%20Kokrajhar%20during%20his%20posting%20there.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F84823%2Fhow-reduce-illiteracy-rates-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20sitting%20passively%20in%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20teacher%20would%20be%20doing%20the%20speaking%3B%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20the%20children%20were%20often%20even%20understanding%20what%20was%20happening.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probing%20and%20conversations%20with%20the%20students%20revealed%20there%20was%20a%20language%20barrier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20were%20used%20to%20speaking%20one%20language%20at%20home%20and%20were%20being%20taught%20in%20a%20different%20language%20in%20school.%20There%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jhingran%20adds%20that%20the%20paucity%20of%20educational%20facilities%2C%20compounded%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20children%20only%20spoke%20the%20tribal%20dialect%2C%20was%20slow-rippling%20into%20illiteracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhir%20Jhingran%20is%20attempting%20to%20bridge%20the%20gaps%20that%20exist%20in%20foundational%20literacy%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDhir%20Jhingran%20is%20attempting%20to%20bridge%20the%20gaps%20that%20exist%20in%20foundational%20literacy%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20extrapolated%20this%20to%20other%20tribal%20belts%20and%20remote%20areas%20of%20India%2C%20he%20found%20the%20situation%20there%20too%20mirrored%20Kokrajhar%E2%80%99s%20reality.%20There%20was%20a%20fast%20widening%20educational%20chasm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJhingran%20devised%20a%20three-step%20approach%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem.%20At%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20these%20pathways%2C%20as%20Jhingran%20calls%20them%2C%20converge%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F458364%2Fmitti-ka-ghar-in-bhopal-by-muskaan-ngo-sustainable-architecture-to-help-denotified-tribes-pardhi-and-gondi-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20a%20generation%20of%20students%20who%20can%20read%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20write%2C%20and%20think.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20more%20about%20the%20three%20approaches%2C%20he%20says%20the%20first%20is%20a%20continuous%20string%20of%20in-person%20workshops%2C%20online%20courses%2C%20and%20cluster%20meetings%20that%20bolster%20teachers%E2%80%99%20confidence%3B%20then%20follows%20collaborations%20with%20government%20agencies%20to%20help%20mainstream%20best%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20MoUs%20have%20been%20signed%20with%20state%20governments%20of%20Assam%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Thirdly%2C%20teachers%20are%20equipped%20with%20workbooks%2C%20guides%2C%20handbooks%2C%20and%20targeted%20daily%20lesson%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20interactive%20teaching%20approaches%2C%20workbooks%20and%20discussions%20students%20are%20taught%20concepts%20that%20they%20may%20have%20otherwise%20found%20difficult%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-1-1752495539-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20interactive%20teaching%20approaches%2C%20workbooks%2C%20and%20discussions%2C%20students%20are%20taught%20concepts%20that%20may%20have%20been%20difficult.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20is%20chequered.%20Jhingran%20has%20spent%20a%20decade%20working%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20to%20improve%20literacy%20programmes%3B%20worked%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Human%20Resource%20Development%2C%20during%20which%20he%20supervised%20and%20coordinated%20the%20District%20Primary%20Education%20Program%20(DPEP)%20in%20eight%20states%3B%20led%20the%20Government%20of%20India-United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Joint%20Program%20for%20Primary%20Education%20in%20eight%20Indian%20states%3B%20was%20National%20Education%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20Nepal%20and%20was%20senior%20advisor%20(education)%2C%20UNICEF%2C%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F456275%2Fsabar-children-swapnaloke-donation-500-rupees-education-food-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efoundational%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20children%20is%20crucial%2C%20he%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20one%20vein%20in%20the%20growing%20ebb%20of%20the%20literacy%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20about%20adult%20literacy%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%E2%80%99s%20Kokrajhar%20was%20once%20notorious%20for%20ethnic%20clashes.%20This%20was%20around%20the%20same%20time%20that%20Jhingran%20was%20posted%20there.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20disturbed%20district.%20I%20was%20posted%20there%20to%20control%20the%20violence.%20While%20law%20and%20order%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20priority%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20literacy%20campaign%20which%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20state%20government%2C%20but%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20implemented.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuxtaposed%20against%20the%20violence%2C%20Jhingran%20noticed%20the%20quiet%20hope%20that%20people%20carried%20%E2%80%94%20the%20desire%20to%20learn.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20parts%20where%20the%20administration%20could%20not%20even%20reach%3B%20schools%20were%20shut.%20But%20I%20got%20the%20feeling%20that%20people%20wanted%20development%2C%20they%20wanted%20their%20children%20to%20get%20educated%2C%20they%20wanted%20peace.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20formalising%20the%20education%20system%20while%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20population%20was%20holed%20up%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F91635%2Fletters-of-love-syrian-refugee-kids-postcards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefugee%20camps%3C%2Fa%3E%20seemed%20counterintuitive.%20Jhingran%2C%20however%2C%20thought%20differently%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20believed%20that%20bringing%20back%20peace%20and%20a%20literacy%20campaign%20should%20be%20woven%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20multilingualism%20becomes%20a%20tool%20rather%20than%20a%20spoke%20in%20the%20wheel%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-2-1752495639-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20multilingualism%20becomes%20a%20tool%20rather%20than%20a%20spoke%20in%20the%20wheel%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20literacy%20campaign%2C%20he%20shares%20how%20it%20targeted%20adults%20aged%2015%20to%2045%20years%2C%20intending%20to%20help%20them%20learn%20to%20read%20and%20write.%20Teaching%20adults%20meant%20recalibrating%20the%20fundamental%20yardsticks%20of%20basic%20education.%20The%20goal%20was%20hefty%2C%20but%20not%20impossible.%20Jhingran%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20created%20a%20team%20of%203%2C000%20volunteers%20in%20the%20district.%20Mainly%20youth%20%E2%80%94%20young%20women%20%E2%80%94%20these%20were%20people%20who%20came%20forward%20volunteering%20to%20conduct%20literacy%20classes%20for%20the%20adults.%20In%20the%20bargain%2C%20we%20also%20made%20them%20agents%20of%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20songs%20composed%20in%20tribal%20dialect%20to%20peace%20committee%20meetings%2C%20a%20proper%20plan%20was%20instated.%20And%2C%20in%20nine%20months%2C%20the%20violence%20gave%20way%20to%20peace.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F449043%2Ftwo-women-yuva-madhavi-teaching-school-dropouts-street-children-hyderabad-chotuu-ki-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20quality%20school%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jhingran%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20demanded%20that%20schools%20improve%2C%20teachers%20attend%20school%20regularly%2C%20that%20school%20building%20infrastructure%20be%20improved%2C%20and%20children%20actually%20learn.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20authorities%20remarked%20on%20the%20campaign%E2%80%99s%20success.%20Uddalak%20Datta%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Assam%20civil%20service%20and%20an%20extra%20assistant%20commissioner%20(EAC)%20of%20Kokrajhar%20at%20the%20time%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20something%20so%20transformational%20could%20happen%20in%20the%20system.%20Kokrajhar%20district%20was%20affected%20by%20extremism.%20People%20were%20so%20scared%2C%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20stay%20there%20because%20of%20the%20violence.%20But%20Jhingran%20transformed%20their%20mindsets.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CJhingran%20inspired%20everyone.%20He%20involved%20everyone.%20He%20saw%20who%20could%20work%20in%20which%20department%20of%20the%20campaign.%20People%20found%20a%20leader%20who%20could%20really%20motivate%20them%20and%20mobilise%20them.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20grand%20success%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20vibrant%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20campaign%20affirmed%20Jhingran%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20antidote%20to%20educational%20precarity%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20what%20is%20taught%20to%20a%20child%20cannot%20fit%20into%20the%20binary%20of%20their%20native%20language%20and%20the%20mode%20of%20instruction%20in%20school%20(often%20English).%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20Jhingran%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%3B%20the%20view%20is%20also%20shared%20by%20the%20United%20Nations.%20A%20UN%20article%2C%20estimating%20that%20at%20least%20half%20of%20the%20global%20population%20is%20bilingual%2C%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmother%20language-based%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400360%2Fmahmood-akram-languages-youth-world-record-prodigy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultilingual%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20fundamental%20to%20achieving%20quality%2C%20inclusive%20learning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20underscored%20that%20students%20learn%20best%20in%20a%20language%20they%20understand%2C%20and%20that%20children%20who%20speak%20the%20language%20they%20are%20taught%20in%20are%2014%20percent%20more%20likely%20to%20read%20with%20understanding%20at%20the%20end%20of%20primary%2C%20compared%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not.%20But%20the%20irony%2C%20the%20report%20highlighted%2C%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9C40%20percent%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20an%20education%20in%20a%20language%20they%20speak%20or%20understand%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-4_11zon-1752495955.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Along%20with%20foundational%20literacy%20even%20gaps%20in%20adult%20literacy%20need%20to%20be%20tackled%20for%20true%20change%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-4_11zon-1752495955.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-4_11zon-1752495955-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-4_11zon-1752495955-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-4_11zon-1752495955-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy-4_11zon-1752495955-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-469663%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAlong%20with%20foundational%20literacy%20even%20gaps%20in%20adult%20literacy%20need%20to%20be%20tackled%20for%20true%20change%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20multilingualism%20becomes%20a%20tool%20rather%20than%20a%20spoke%20in%20the%20wheel%20at%20the%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20Jhingran%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20lot%20of%20primary%20classrooms%2C%20children%20stay%20silent%3B%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20speak%20at%20all%3B%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20express%20themselves.%20We%20stress%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F187074%2F4-awesome-education-systems-from-across-the-world-that-india-can-learn-from%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20the%20oral%20language%20strong%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20accordingly%2C%20written%20and%20spoken%20language%20will%20also%20become%20strong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelling%20the%20success%20story%20of%20Sapna%20(name%20changed%20on%20request)%2C%20a%20seven-year-old%20from%20Haryana%2C%20whose%20mother%20tongue%20was%20a%20dialect%20of%20Punjabi%2C%20Jhingran%20recalls%20how%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20bright%20child%2C%20she%20was%20a%20passi