osting%20community%20workshops%20on%20sustainable%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stay%20that%20teaches%20you%20to%20slow%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retreat%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20%E2%80%98Kosen%20Rufu%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20a%20Japanese%20phrase%20meaning%20%E2%80%98peace%20and%20happiness%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20Buddhist%20practice.%20True%20to%20its%20name%2C%20the%20homestay%20offers%20little%20by%20way%20of%20luxury%20as%20conventionally%20defined.%20There%20are%20no%20TVs%2C%20no%20air%20conditioning%2C%20and%20often%2C%20no%20mobile%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20guests%20find%20mud%20cottages%20warmed%20by%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20scent%20of%20pine%20wood%2C%20and%20views%20that%20stretch%20beyond%20the%20folds%20of%20the%20mountains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20no%20scaffolding%20like%20you%E2%80%99d%20see%20in%20cities.%20Most%20of%20the%20work%20was%20done%20by%20local%20artisans%20using%20traditional%20tools.%20It%20was%20a%20collective%20memory%20%E2%80%94%20something%20modern%20design%20has%20almost%20forgotten%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naresh%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20here%20and%20at%20first%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20unsettled%20by%20the%20quiet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manju.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20by%20the%20end%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20leave.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20weekend%20getaway%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20will%20recharge%20your%20soul.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T190116.163-1752241146.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe