402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183537.707-1752240191-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECelebrated%20actor%20and%20lyricist%20Piyush%20Mishra%20was%20all%20praise%20about%20Kosen%20Rufu.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20sustainability%20costs%20and%20saves%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20retreat%20of%20this%20kind%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20cheap.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20nearly%2030%25%20over%20budget%20from%20our%20planned%20%E2%82%B92%E2%80%932.5%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20never%20considered%20cutting%20corners.%E2%80%9D%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20investment%20has%20paid%20off%2C%20not%20just%20in%20guest%20satisfaction%2C%20but%20in%20minimal%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20Didi%20Contractor%E2%80%99s%20construction%20techniques%2C%20the%20mud%20walls%20are%20resilient%20through%20the%20seasons.%20The%20natural%20plasters%20used%2C%20involving%20pine%20needles%20and%20multiple%20binding%20layers%2C%20have%20kept%20out%20seepage%20and%20cracks.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20to%20spend%20on%20repairs%20the%20way%20you%20would%20with%20concrete%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20saving%2C%20though%2C%20lies%20in%20preserving%20the%20terrain.%20By%20not%20flattening%20land%20or%20using%20heavy%20equipment%2C%20the%20retreat%20has%20avoided%20the%20kind%20of%20erosion%20and%20drainage%20issues%20that%20plague%20many%20mountain%20resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20ahead%20and%20expanding%20with%20caution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20interest%20in%20the%20homestay%20grows%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20considering%20adding%20a%20few%20more%20mud%20cottages%20to%20the%20compound.%20But%20