e%20Aarambh%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98beginning%E2%80%99%20in%20Hindi.%20It%20was%20founded%20by%2027-year-old%20Nishtha%20Chauhan%2C%20an%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20who%20left%20a%20promising%20career%20in%20aerospace%20to%20return%20to%20the%20earth%2C%20quite%20literally.%20Instead%20of%20the%20conventional%20corporate%20path%2C%20Nishtha%20chose%20to%20till%20the%20soil%2C%20grind%20millets%20and%20compost%20kitchen%20scraps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%20is%20not%20a%20spontaneous%20detour.%20Raised%20in%20a%20modest%20Gujarati%20household%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20the%20wisdom%20of%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20millet%20practitioner%20who%20firmly%20believed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271562%2Fchennai-woman-sells-ready-to-eat-snack-mixes-from-ancient-grains%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoodness%20of%20ancient%20grains%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(finger%20millet)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sorghum)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pearl%20millet)%2C%20and%20little%20millet.%20Mealtimes%20at%20home%20were%20simple%20and%20wholesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20grown%20up%20accustomed%20to%20seeing%20all%20the%20kitchen%E2%80%99s%20wet%20waste%20carefully%20composted.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20did%20not%20think%20much%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20once%20I%20became%20an%20adult%20and%20looked%20around%20me%2C%20I%20began%20to%20realise%20just%20how%20deeply%20those%20habits%20were%20ingrained%20in%20me%2C%20and%20how%20important%20they%20really%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20Lalbhai%20Dalpatbhai%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Nishtha%20joined%20Azista%20Aerospace%2C%20where%20she%20worked%20on%20satellite%20payloads%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%20It%20was%20an%20exciting%20work%20which%20was%20intellectually%20demanding%20and%20high-profile.%20But%20amid%20the%20sterile%20labs%20and%20long%20hours%2C%20she%20felt%20increasingly%20disconnected.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nishtha%20Chauhan%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20food%20business%20but%20she%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20can%20help%20the%20society%20and%20the%20environment%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467608%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENishtha%20Chauhan%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20food%20business%2C%20but%20she%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20could%20help%