ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T100847.663_11zon-1752208742-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T100847.663_11zon-1752208742-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T100847.663_11zon-1752208742-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T100847.663_11zon-1752208742-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467640%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EInstead%20of%20air%20conditioners%2C%20the%20cafe%20uses%20water-cooling%20systems%20and%20gentle%20misting%20fans%20to%20keep%20the%20space%20naturally%20cool%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cafe%20also%20avoids%20disposable%20tissues.%20Instead%2C%20there%20is%20a%20handwashing%20station%20with%20a%20handwash%20and%20reusable%20cloth%20towels.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20what%20we%20do%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nishtha%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20wash%20your%20hands%20and%20use%20a%20towel.%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20wanted%20to%20maintain%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETraining%20young%20minds%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20Earth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20factor%20that%20sets%20Cafe%20Aarambh%20apart%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20just%20its%20food%2C%20but%20its%20purpose.%20From%20the%20outset%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20envisioned%20it%20as%20a%20learning%20space%2C%20especially%20for%20children.%20Partnering%20with%20schools%20such%20as%20GEMS%20Genesis%20International%20School%2C%20Adani%20International%2C%20and%20Anand%20Niketan%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20series%20of%20imme