y%20business%20management.%20His%20city%20years%20were%20filled%20with%20building%20startups%20and%20strategic%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20chasing%20success%2C%20but%20somehow%20I%20felt%20disconnected%20from%20people%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20the%20world%20around%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Momo%E2%80%99s%20upbringing%20in%20Pune%20was%20woven%20with%20the%20colourful%20threads%20of%20art%20and%20culture.%20From%20childhood%2C%20she%20indulged%20in%20the%20world%20of%20theatre%20and%20film%2C%20pouring%20her%20heart%20into%20performances%20that%20captivated%20audiences%20and%20brought%20stories%20to%20life.%20Her%20success%20as%20an%20actor%20and%20director%20in%20the%20Marathi%20industry%20brought%20her%20recognition%20and%20the%20thrill%20of%20creative%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20beneath%20the%20applause%20and%20the%20bright%20lights%2C%20she%20felt%20a%20yearning%20that%20went%20beyond%20the%20stage.%20The%20fast%20pace%20of%20the%20entertainment%20world%2C%20with%20its%20relentless%20schedules%20and%20endless%20demands%2C%20left%20little%20room%20for%20stillness%20or%20introspection.%20She%20longed%20for%20a%20life%20uncluttered%20by%20noise%2C%20where%20she%20could%20find%20space%20to%20breathe%20freely%20and%20reconnect%20with%20something%20more%20enduring%20and%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20leave%20my%20passion%20behind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflects%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20I%20needed%20to%20find%20balance%2C%20a%20life%20where%20creativity%20could%20flow%20naturally%2C%20alongside%20peace%20and%20simplicity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20meeting%20of%20minds%20(and%20hearts)%20online%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeil%20and%20Momo%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20in%202015%2C%20through%20a%20matrimonial%20website%2C%20brought%20these%20shared%20longings%20into%20focus.%20%E