hop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T204819.711_11zon-1752247134-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T204819.711_11zon-1752247134-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T204819.711_11zon-1752247134-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T204819.711_11zon-1752247134-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468404%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESince%202023%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20hosting%20immersive%20three-day%20%E2%80%9CIntroduction%20to%20Permaculture%E2%80%9D%20workshops%20for%20interested%20visitors%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrushti%20Gosavi%2C%2026%2C%20a%20homoeopathic%20practitioner%20from%20Nashik%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20I%20have%20been%20drawn%20towards%20a%20more%20natural%20and%20conscious%20way%20of%20living%2C%20largely%20because%20I%20have%20felt%20the%20weight%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20our%20lives%20and%20health.%20The%20idea%20of%20permaculture%20fascinated%20me%20from%20the%20moment%20I%20first%20heard%20about%20it%2C%20and%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Instagram%20algorithm%2C%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20Neil%20%26amp%3B%20Momo%E2%80%99s%20page%20while%20searching%20for%20sustainability%20content.%20I%20have%20been%20following%20them%20since%20the%20very%20beginning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20finally%20made%20it%20to%20their%20March%20workshop%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20stepping%20into%20a%20space%20I%20had%20been%20searching%20for.%20The%20experience%20was%20full%20of%20insight%20on%20sustainable%20practices%20and%20the%20people%20were%20curious%2C%20kind%2C%20and%20had%20similar%20thought%20processes%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20even%20more%20special.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20moments%20for%20me%20was%20learning%20about%20how%20roots%20connect%20underground%20and%20how%20soil%20functions%20much%20like%20the%20human%20body.%20As%20someone%20trained%20in%20homoeopathy%2C%20that%20parallel%20was%20incredibly%20exciting.%20And%20yes%2C%20I%20dug%20my%20hands%20into%20cow%20dung%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20absolutely%20loved%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20impactful%20moments%20during%20the%20workshop%20was%20a%20life%20cycle%20analysis%20(LCA)%20activity%2C%20which%20revealed%20the%20hidden%20environmental%20cost%20of%20everyday%20consumer%20habits.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20really%20hit%20me%2C%20I%20uninstalled%20all%20my%20e-commerce%20apps%20while%20still%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20have%20not%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20go%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoodbye%20apps%2C%20hello%20conscious%20living%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20workshop%2C%20Srushti%20has%20begun%20planning%20a%20green%20space%20of%20her%20own%2C%20with%20native%20trees%2C%20birds%2C%20and%20a%20small%20food-growing%20area.%20A%20chance%20connection%20with%20a%20native%20plant%20expert%20at%20the%20farm%20helped%20her%20finally%20convince%20her%20parents%20that%20native%20plants%20can%20be%20beautiful%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamika%20Bhide%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20playback%20singer%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20attended%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424318%2Ffive-farm-volunteering-opportunities-in-tamil-nadu-auroville-chennai-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epermaculture%20workshop%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20her%20husband%20after%20watching%20one%20of%20Neil%20%26amp%3B%20Momo%E2%80%99s%20interviews%20online.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20fo